text: The Czechoslovakia women's national under-18 and under-19 basketball team was the women's basketball side that represented Czechoslovakia in international under-18 and under-19 competitions. \- Czechoslovakia women's national junior basketball team, FIBA.com, Retrieved 27 July 2016.After the country was peacefully dissolved in 1993, the team was succeeded by separate Czech and Slovak teams. == See also == * Czechoslovakia national basketball team * Czechoslovakia women's national basketball team ==References== == External links == * (en) Czechoslovakia, archive.fiba.com Category:Basketball in Czechoslovakia Category:Former national basketball teams Category:Women's national under-19 basketball teams W
